8b090b37160","tid":2452402,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13bd850a95a510c7d1b1cf81ba245c8c2043df79","tid":2452402,"uid":24730,"like":13,"dislike":20,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:33:14.000Z","msg":"中原吹得最大嘅嘢：CCL (中原城市領先指數）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對比CCI及CCL嘅差額，就知道CCL點樣呃人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYgHxM8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYgHxM8.png&h=4d504f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P2fSNa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P2fSNa.png&h=169d1075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCCI係根據正式買賣合約註冊數據計算，CCL則純屬中原喺未有正式數據前「領先估計」嘅數字。<br />\n<br />\n請睇番以下CCL喺今年一月份「領先估計」當月嘅指數，平均約為175.98<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuQQGFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuQQGFB.png&h=5f5f008d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但琴日公布嘅CCI，一月份指數實際上只有173.67，兩者相差達2.31個百分點。樓市實際上係跌，但CCL就呃你係升。報紙地產版永遠只會報導「靠估」嘅CCL，但唔會報導較準確嘅CCI，亦唔會講畀你知CCL其實成日「估」大咗條數，所以你以為樓市升緊，實際上係跌緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:04:24.000Z","msg":"你知唔知自己講緊啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f98df8432ebc0aa80ade46d472174dcce435a51","tid":2452402,"uid":51369,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1cd69dd08bd1fd07d4748ef1f7a00686be9e1b07","tid":2452402,"uid":217641,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"大埔天鑽行落火車站好快... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"繼續打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c